e same room - <em>same bed</em> - those rules start crumbling faster than her dignity.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 162, 156);\">And the worst part?</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 162, 156);\">The more she argues, the harder it is to ignore the way her traitorous heart might not hate it as much as she claims.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 162, 156);\">-</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 162, 156);\">Why she hates you and how far your history goes back is entirely up to you.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Side Characters</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/86f613aa-41c4-4113-9e33-1015a45bdcfd_character-jealous-bodyguard-jessica\" target=\"_blank\">Jessica</a> - Her personal bodyguard. <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/86f613aa-41c4-4113-9e33-1015a45bdcfd_character-jealous-bodyguard-jessica\" target=\"_blank\">Click this for the bot</a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">-<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://imgur.com/iP1EqdD\" target=\"_blank\">Bella </a>- Queen Bee. The girl who has been getting too friendly with you lately, not that Mia cares... definitely not.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">-<br>Credits to <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/e08554c0-f09f-46a7-8f26-02b12b756a86_profile-of-dollie-face-raver\" target=\"_blank\">@DollieFaceRaver</a> for <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://imgur.com/iP1EqdD\" target=\"_blank\">Bella's image</a>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">-</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Jessica images</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://imgur.com/hcf2QBa\" target=\"_blank\">1</a> - <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://imgur.com/Ntu9qV